  61:../../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/adc.h ****     /** 
  62:../../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/adc.h ****     Initializes a single ADC pin as a Multiplexed ADC.
  63:../../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/adc.h ****     Requires a CD405X Multiplexer connected to the pin.
  64:../../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/adc.h ****     You only need to supply the mux pins that are required,
  65:../../../libs/libDaisy/src/per/adc.h ****     e.g. a 4052 mux would only require mux_0 and mux_1.
